      <title>中国人民银行准备通过银行发行数十亿元人民币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/china-central-bank-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国人民银行表示，目前已通过与贷方达成的协议，拥有“数千亿”人民币国债可供使用，央行旨在为创纪录的涨势降温。彭博电视台的吉尔·迪西斯报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/china-central-bank-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:39:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国人民银行准备通过各大银行发行数十亿元人民币债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国央行采取了进一步措施，通过出售国债来冷却创纪录的股市上涨，并表示目前通过与贷款机构达成的协议，央行可以持有“数千亿元”人民币的国债。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/pboc-readies-hundreds-of-billions-of-yuan-bond-sale-capacity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 01:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里昂证券：三星电子未来几个季度盈利和股价将表现良好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/samsung-profit-stock-to-do-well-in-quarters-ahead-clsa-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里昂证券韩国研究主管 Sanjeev Rana 讨论了三星电子的前景，这家全球最大的内存芯片和智能手机制造商公布了多年来最快的利润增长速度，Rana 在“彭博：亚洲交易”节目中发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-05/samsung-profit-stock-to-do-well-in-quarters-ahead-clsa-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 00:24:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛和花旗预测 Nvidia 供应商海力士股价上涨 90% 后将进一步上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/hynix-s-90-share-gain-is-just-getting-started-for-goldman-citi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国 SK 海力士公司是 Nvidia Corp. 的主要供应商，其股价在过去一年中上涨了 90% 以上，华尔街预测该公司股价还将进一步上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-05/hynix-s-90-share-gain-is-just-getting-started-for-goldman-citi</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大有条件批准嘉能可的泰克煤矿交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/glencore-s-teck-coal-unit-deal-is-said-to-near-canada-approval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大政府批准嘉能可公司（Glencore Plc）以 69 亿美元收购泰克资源有限公司（Teck Resources Ltd.）的冶金煤业务，但附加了若干严格条件，以保护当地的就业和环境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/glencore-s-teck-coal-unit-deal-is-said-to-near-canada-approval</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 23:38:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飓风风险和美国库存下降导致油价接近两个月高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[飓风贝丽尔预示着风暴季节可能会更加糟糕，而美国原油库存减少暗示需求增加，油价交易价格接近两个月高点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 23:37:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本家庭支出下降，经济增长前景不明朗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/japan-s-household-spending-falls-clouding-growth-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本5月份家庭支出意外下降，增加了消费不再是第二季度经济主要推动力的可能性，也使央行下次加息的前景变得复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/japan-s-household-spending-falls-clouding-growth-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 23:33:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业数据公布前全球股市触及峰值：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/asian-equities-to-tread-water-before-us-jobs-data-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员将注意力转向周五将公布的美国就业数据，以寻找美联储降息的线索，全球股市有望守住周四创下的历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/asian-equities-to-tread-water-before-us-jobs-data-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 22:19:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本消费类股票将因工资上涨而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/japan-s-consumer-stocks-to-get-boost-as-wage-increases-kick-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些投资者表示，随着工资上涨引发的消费复苏迹象开始显现，日本落后的消费类股票可能在今年下半年得到提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/japan-s-consumer-stocks-to-get-boost-as-wage-increases-kick-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党有望获胜，富时 100 指数期货上涨，英镑保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/pound-steady-as-labour-projected-to-win-majority-in-uk-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国出口民调显示工党将确保其长期预测的压倒性选举胜利，而基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 有望凭借更大的经济稳定承诺成为首相，英国股票期货随之上涨，英镑保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/pound-steady-as-labour-projected-to-win-majority-in-uk-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:08:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
